<p><strong>Seeking Greenlight</strong>: Yes</p>
<p><strong>Page Type:</strong> SCP article</p>
<p><strong>Genre</strong>: Horror</p>
<p><strong>Elevator Pitch:</strong></p>
<p>An entity that appears to its victims in weird recurring dreams. Once it has chosen a victim, the entity wil subject them to personalized dreams designed to trick them into consenting to having their personality eaten. A victim who has gone through this process will loose memories, distinctive character traits and their overall sense of self. At the end of the process, the victim is left an empty shell (no memories or personality whatsoever). The entity has guided humanity to consciousness and organized society in order to harvest and eat our personalities.</p>
<p><strong>Central Narrative:</strong></p>
<p>Through interviews with the victims and a dream journal the foundation pieces toghether who/what is the entity. At the end the foundation deduces that the entity feeds off personalities. We also discover that the victims are persuaded in their dreams to consent to being eaten through manipulation and deception. It seems that this entity is connected to the rise of consciousness in humans who has bred this trait in us like cattle to harvest. The foundation must then supply a more or less steady stream of tasty D-class in order to keep all victims accounted for.</p>
<p><strong>Hook/Attention-Grabber:</strong></p>
<p>In this entry, what makes humanity special on planet earth is simply something this entity bred in humans through our dreams in order to hunt us for sport and sustenance. The entity itself also will have an unsettling atmosphere using its victims memories, fears and quirks in order to &quot;eat&quot; them.</p>
<p><strong>Additional Notes:</strong></p>
<p>Containment procedures:<br />
-Finding eligible D-class and feeding them to the entity.<br />
-Finding and dealing with any other victims outside of foundation control.</p>
<p>There will be an MTF involved in the article that specializes in &quot;onironautics&quot; (advanced lucid dreaming).</p>

